<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="H" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Hum3" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Hum,</orth> interj., an exclamation expressive of deliberation: <bibl n="shak. wiv 3.5.141" default="NO" valid="yes">Wiv. III, 5, 141</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 1h4 3.1.158" default="NO" valid="yes">H4A III, 1, 158</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tro 3.3.282" default="NO" valid="yes">Troil. III, 3, 282</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tro 3.3.282" default="NO" valid="yes">Troil. III, 3, 282</bibl> <bibl n="shak. tim 2.2.204" default="NO" valid="yes">Tim. II, 2, 204</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tim 3.3.1" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 3, 1</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tim 3.3.1" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 3, 1</bibl> <bibl n="shak. mac 4.3.203" default="NO" valid="yes">Mcb. IV, 3, 203</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ham 2.2.617" default="NO" valid="yes">Hml. II, 2, 617</bibl> (Ff om.). <bibl n="shak. ham 5.1.112" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 1, 112</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. lr 1.2.58" default="NO" valid="yes">Lr. I, 2, 58</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. lr 3.4.48" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 4, 48</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. oth 5.2.36" default="NO" valid="yes">Oth. V, 2, 36</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. cym 3.5.103" default="NO" valid="yes">Cymb. III, 5, 103</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. per 5.1.84" default="NO" valid="yes">Per. V, 1, 84</bibl>. Substantively: <cit><quote>the shrug, the h. or ha,</quote> <bibl n="shak. wt 2.1.71" default="NO" valid="yes">Wint. II, 1, 71</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>these --s and ha's,</quote> <bibl n="shak. wt 2.1.71" default="NO" valid="yes">Wint. II, 1, 71</bibl></cit> <cit><quote>his h. is a battery,</quote> <bibl n="shak. cor 5.4.22" default="NO" valid="yes">Cor. V, 4, 22</bibl></cit>.
